dct_title_s: S. Rom. Imperii Circuli Et Electoratus Bavariae Tabula Chorographica
dct_alternative_sm: Sacri Romani Imperii Circuli Et Electoratus Bavariae Tabula Chorographica
dct_description_sm: Georg Philippus Finckh, invenit ac fecit Ao. 1663, Revidit Ao. 1671. Effigiem Amling sculp.
Relief shown by shading and pictorially.
Bar scale on map given in "Miliare Germano Bavaricum".
Coat of arms, compass rose, winds, cherubs, lions.
Appears in Finckh's Bavariae geographica descriptio, 1684.
